Diamond::

She guided the pod back to the Allience hanger bay.  She landed and 
shut down the pod. She smiled, then chuckled. She always felt good 
after a kill.  She got up and walked out of the pod.  She went over 
to the hanger entrance and opened her link. "Zardus, I have returned 
to you."  She walked down the all and went to the messhall.  She got 
a strong glass of liquid energon and downed the whole glass in one 
gulp.  She smiled and put the glass down.  She headed to the lab.
